## 🧩 Widget & Bileşen Kalıpları

### AppCard (Beyaz kart)
```dart
// lib/core/glass_container.dart içinde AppCard widget'ı mevcut
AppCard(
  padding: const EdgeInsets.all(AppLayout.cardPadding),
  margin: const EdgeInsets.only(bottom: AppLayout.sectionGap),
  child: ...,
)

// Manuel Container gerektiğinde:
Container(
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: AppTheme.bgCard,
    borderRadius: AppRadius.cardRadius,   // 16dp
    boxShadow: AppTheme.shadowCard,
  ),
  padding: const EdgeInsets.all(AppLayout.cardPadding),
)
```

### Primary CTA Butonu
```dart
// Gradient + glow, minimum 52dp yükseklik (Android touch target)
Container(
  width: double.infinity,
  height: AppLayout.listItemHeight,  // 52dp
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    gradient: const LinearGradient(
      colors: [AppTheme.accentViolet, AppTheme.accentPurple],
