### BottomNavigationBar / NavigationBar (M3)
```dart
// Material 3 NavigationBar kullan (NavigationBar widget'ı)
NavigationBar(
  backgroundColor: AppTheme.bgCard,
  indicatorColor: AppTheme.accentViolet.withOpacity(0.12),
  labelTextStyle: MaterialStateProperty.resolveWith((states) {
    if (states.contains(MaterialState.selected)) {
      return const TextStyle(color: AppTheme.accentViolet, fontSize: 11, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600);
    }
    return const TextStyle(color: AppTheme.textTertiary, fontSize: 11);
  }),
  destinations: const [
    NavigationDestination(
      icon: Icon(Icons.home_outlined),
      selectedIcon: Icon(Icons.home_rounded, color: AppTheme.accentViolet),
      label: 'Ana Sayfa',
    ),
    // ...
  ],
)
```

### Snackbar / Hata Bildirimi
```dart
// flutter-rule.mdc'ye göre: SnackBar yerine SelectableText.rich kullan
// Ancak sistem bildirimleri için ScaffoldMessenger gerekiyorsa:
ScaffoldMessenger.of(context).showSnackBar(
